Manchester United host Manchester City in the derby at Old Trafford on Sunday . 
  Louis van Gaal and Manuel Pellegrini are in contrasting form ahead of the derby . 
  Sportsmail have selected a composite XI of the two sides . 
  David de Gea and Pablo Zabaleta start in goal for United . 
  Wayne Rooney and Ander Herrera start in midfield for the Red Devils . 
 